    {
      "id": "PopularPost346429",
      "post_content": "Hmm, this card is just not flexible or fast enough. Yes, I get that Shivan Dragon was similar, but A) powercreep, B) this is a 4/4, not a 5/5, and doesn't have flying, C) it's red/white as opposed to mono-red, and D) powercreep.  \n  \nTo stay within the curve and really excite Boros players, this needs more gas. Haste, and the ability to split the damage as you choose, would have worked better, allowing it to be a satisfying top to a Boros mana curve, with the ability to win games the turn it comes into play if the opponent has not developed a robust enough board presence.  \n  \nAs it is, it's a slow beater that MIGHT take out a threat when it enters play, and then requires far too much mana to make it worth its cost. Leave it behind. ",
      "posted_by": "Wulfsten",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost346429\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Hmm, this card is just not flexible or fast enough. Yes, I get that Shivan Dragon was similar, but A) powercreep, B) this is a 4/4, not a 5/5, and doesn't have flying, C) it's red/white as opposed to mono-red, and D) powercreep.<br/><br/>To stay within the curve and really excite Boros players, this needs more gas. Haste, and the ability to split the damage as you choose, would have worked better, allowing it to be a satisfying top to a Boros mana curve, with the ability to win games the turn it comes into play if the opponent has not developed a robust enough board presence.<br/><br/>As it is, it's a slow beater that MIGHT take out a threat when it enters play, and then requires far too much mana to make it worth its cost. Leave it behind. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '346429'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy62217\">Wulfsten</span>\r\n                                (10/17/2013 5:52:15 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\"